---
import HomeStatusCard from '../components/HomeStatusCard.vue';
import AppLayout from '../layouts/AppLayout.astro';
---

<AppLayout
  title="go-web-server web frontend"
  description="Astro + Vue auth shell for the go-web-server frontend migration."
>
  <section class="page-intro stack-md">
    <p class="eyebrow">Astro + Vue browser path</p>
    <h1>go-web-server frontend migration</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      The new browser shell is now handling home and auth flows in the staged <code>web/</code>
      workspace while the Go backend keeps sessions, CSRF, and PostgreSQL in place.
    </p>
  </section>

  <HomeStatusCard client:load />
</AppLayout>
